msg: QPID-2346 : AcknowledgeAfterFailoverTest was putting more messages on the external broker than the testing AcknowledgeTest code was expecting. Additionally when run in the java-derby(persistent) case the unacknowledge messages were recovered when the broker was restarted. To address this the store of each broker is deleted when the it is stopped.
To ensure that the persistent tests do not impact each other enabled the broker.clean.between.tests on the java-derby profile
